  "markdown": "![Khadoom](<Base64-Image-Removed>)\n\n- About me\n- Features\n- Customer reviews\n- Contact us\n- Faqs\n- Blog\n- Terms & conditions\n\nChat with me\n\n![Khadoom](<Base64-Image-Removed>)\n\nHi I'm\n\nKhadoom\n\n![Banner 1](https://khadoom.ai/static/media/Image%202.b31e73f804000423d903.png)\n\n![Banner 2](https://khadoom.ai/static/media/Image%204.f8b5cb9c9ad05d10a6c0.png)\n\n![Banner 3](https://khadoom.ai/static/media/Image%203.4607c13e562ce21d9fc3.png)\n\nYour friendly\n\nA.I powered\n\nAssistant\n\nI'm Khadoom, Qatar's first\n\nAI-powered personal assistant,\n\ndesigned to ease and simplify\n\ncustomers' lives. In operation\n\nacross Qatar,I fulfill every task that\n\ncustomers need completed-from on-demand delivery, to pet services,\n\nto grocery & personal shopping and much more.\n\nYour life just got easier.\n\nKnow more\n\n![](https://khadoom.ai/static/media/fea-msg.616f5b05375276faa1db.png)\n\n![](https://khadoom.ai/static/media/fea-dots.3c39ac4a956ed44efcc2.png)\n\n![](https://khadoom.ai/static/media/khadoom-phone.0421ddd8c38322ec1605.png)\n\nFeatures\n\n![](https://khadoom.ai/static/media/personal-img.06179b5bc57069d2f25c.png)\n\nPersonal\n\nShopping\n\n![](https://khadoom.ai/static/media/parcel-img.b734dce93d5a5ce57de9.png)\n\nParcel\n\nDelivery\n\n![](https://khadoom.ai/static/media/laundry-img.08b3b4d5b7c9a3a19286.png)\n\nLaundry pick up &\n\nDrop off\n\n![](https://khadoom.ai/static/media/pet-img.4cc36cebb8920ff41025.png)\n\nPet pick up &\n\nDrop off\n\nPrice starts from\n\n10 Qr\n\nI can fulfill a variety of tasks and chores for our customers. A few examples of such tasks are on-demand delivery, personal shopping (groceries, clothing, electronics, beauty products, and more), parcel & laundry pick up, pet services, and delivery of food, gifts, documents & medication. If you are unsure the task can be done, all you have to do is text me on WhatsApp and I will confirm.\n\n![](<Base64-Image-Removed>)\n\nContact us\n\nI am Khadoom. Whatever language you speak, I can\n\nunderstand and whatever task you need I can get done!\n\nContact me on WhatsApp for all your daily chores\n\nand leave the rest up to me.\n\nLusail, Qatar\n\n![](https://khadoom.ai/static/media/phone-icon.b0e9e0e54848e9b5c5f76a41f4fad4bd.svg)+974 7444 7766\n\ninfo@khadoom.ai\n\nSend\n\n![](<Base64-Image-Removed>)\n\nFREQUENTLY\n\nASKED QUESTIONS\n\nWho is Khadoom?\n\nKhadoom is me! A personal assistant powered by AI to fulfill daily tasks for customers.\n\nHow much does Khadoom cost?\n\nPrice is calculated according to the distance traveled. My rates start at 10 QAR.\n\nHow far can Khadoom deliver to or pick up from?\n\nI operate across Qatar with an open delivery zone. No place is too remote for me as long as the location is reachable using regular navigation systems.\n\nI need a driver to do several stops. Is that possible?\n\nOf course! When you contact me on WhatsApp, you can mention all the chores and stops you need, and I'll assign you the right driver.\n\nhow can I contact Khadoom?\n\nContact me on WhatsApp at +97474447766. Just send a text message or voice message and I will fulfill your tasks!\n\nWhat forms of payment do you accept?\n\nI accept Apple Pay, Google Pay, NAPS/Debit/Credit Card, and cash.\n\n![](https://khadoom.ai/static/media/faq1_img.266930cb81903aeeb0bb.png)![](https://khadoom.ai/static/media/faq2_img.589234013eeaa360a7d6.png)![](https://khadoom.ai/static/media/faq3_img.3d1968ca8f36ad241a18.png)\n\n![Khadoom](<Base64-Image-Removed>)\n\nI am Khadoom. Whatever language you speak, I can\n\nunderstand and whatever task you need I can get done!\n\nContact me on WhatsApp for all your daily chores\n\nand leave the rest up to me.\n\nHome\n\nAbout me\n\nFeatures\n\nContact us\n\nContact\n\nLusail, Qatar\n\nInfo@khadoom.ai+974 7444 7766",
